summary: A gore player house in Falkreath with everything you need to travel skyrim as a powerfull dark mage.
descriptionHtml:
A gore player house in Falkreath with everything you need (white robes and armor/robe with strong enchantment, new spells...) to travel skyrim as a powerfull dark mage.

Look for an uncommon grave in Falkreath cemetery, there is a map marker.

If you have any problem, suggest or question please contact me, but only directly. Remember i never read comments, i never participate to forums, neither steam communnity or social networks, and i have no intention to do it.

Feel free to use and change any parts of this mod
author: Leucippe
